{"tid":2456091,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港多youtuber係一件好事 起碼對我黎講","createTime":"2021-03-21T15:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T17:50:40.000Z","uid":98473,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a277472a02d839d3f723f2cfdc3f92b8b6ab6d01","tid":2456091,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"我係一個好鐘意睇廣東話片既人黎<br />\n但有時又唔想太投入去睇戲/劇<br />\n所我係好鐘意求其開個youtuber黎播<br />\n當係電台咁聽<br />\n乜片都鐘意睇 最緊要係廣東話<br />\n見到d岩岩新人做youtuber既 都會好開心 想同佢打氣<br />\n見到有人賣廣告 我會好開心 即係佢有錢賺<br />\n因為明明我一蚊都冇比過 但佢就無條件咁拍片剪片<br />\n咁可能你話佢賣廣告喎 佢有賺錢喎<br />\n屌 咁我事實一蚊都唔洗比 就有得睇片 關我撚事<br />\n你覺得唔好睇咪轉第個睇 或者比個dislike<br />\n都唔知有乜好嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明可以百花齊放 係要搞到要批鬥邊個邊個好低質 <br />\n邊個邊個賣廣告咁<br />\n當然 屎家軍 藍絲個d垃圾就真係需要屌"},{"pid":"e471e409cf067d0a4ddf7c88f31b755af9c1bbce","tid":2456091,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8df3d790f106817be417a3f7b17723d16e6c89c","tid":2456091,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:01:58.000Z","msg":"咁借個位黎<br />\n大家一齊做起黃營YOUTUBER<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n突發: 請大家盡力懲罰以下黃色Channel今個星期出嘅片(11-3-2021 至 18-3-2021)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gLNyJS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gLNyJS</a>"},{"pid":"69b943370a48a772d81aaf1626abb28fca29ac41","tid":2456091,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:03:27.000Z","msg":"真 淨係想聽母語 其他個啲youtuber完全冇興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d1469b8b02b33835b9695aa4e01f5afd1d095a","tid":2456091,"uid":387033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T17